net.sf.jkniv.whinstone.jdbc.result

Class PojoResultRow<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jkniv.whinstone.jdbc.result.PojoResultRow<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - generic type of Class object to inject value of ResultSet
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.sf.jkniv.sqlegance.ResultRow<T,java.sql.ResultSet>

    public class PojoResultRow<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.sf.jkniv.sqlegance.ResultRow<T,java.sql.ResultSet>
    Inject the ResultSet at flat Object, basic types like: String, Date, Numbers, Clob, Blob...

    This class doesn't supports inject value at Oriented-Object model, like nested objects.

    Author:
    Alisson Gomes
